# Evaluation

The system was evaluated using human-coded qualitative transcript annotations from the ENVIO research workflow.

The evaluation framework compares:

- LLM-generated coding
- human qualitative annotations
- No-RAG vs Contextual RAG pipelines

using structured sentence-aligned evaluation.

---

## Evaluation Metrics

The system supports:

- Macro F1
- Cohen’s Kappa
- category-level agreement
- RAG vs No-RAG comparison
- qualitative coding consistency analysis

---

## Experimental Configuration

| Component | Setting |
|---|---|
| Human Alignment | Enabled |
| Batch Coding | Enabled |
| Batch Size | 5 |
| Contextual RAG | Enabled |
| RAG Window | Previous + Current + Next Batch |
| RAG Context Limit | 2000 chars |
| Evaluation Type | Sentence-aligned |

